{{!
    @template local_dimensions/central/structure_related_modal

    Body of the referenced-competency modal on the Structure tab: the same competency
    detail card as the inline pane (shared local_dimensions/central/structure_detail_content
    partial) so the visual is identical, wrapped so it fills the dialog with its own close
    button. The metric counters render as plain, non-interactive numbers (linksclickable off)
    to avoid opening a usage modal over this one, and the referenced-competencies section is
    omitted (showrelated off). Populated client-side by local_dimensions/central/structure
    from the local_dimensions_get_structure_node web service response.

    Context variables required:
    * detailconfig (object) {linksclickable, showrelated} · always {false, false} here

    Example context (json):
    {
        "detailconfig": {"linksclickable": false, "showrelated": false}
    }
}}
<div class="local-dimensions-central-plans-detail local-dimensions-central-structure-detail local-dimensions-related-modal-card">
    <button type="button" class="local-dimensions-related-modal-close" data-action="close-related-modal"
            aria-label="{{#str}}closebuttontitle{{/str}}">
        <i class="fa fa-times" aria-hidden="true"></i>
    </button>
    <div data-region="detail-content">
        {{#detailconfig}}
        {{> local_dimensions/central/structure_detail_content }}
        {{/detailconfig}}
    </div>
</div>
